    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Clothing meant for travelling. Particularly in reference to clothing from the 19th century onwards; the clothing typically reflects what is suitable for a particular means of transportation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
